<div class="min-h-screen bg-gray-900 pt-24 pb-12 relative overflow-hidden text-gray-300">
  <!-- Dynamic Background -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[#0a0a0a] z-0"></div>
  
  <!-- Grid Pattern -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[url('https://grainy-gradients.vercel.app/noise.svg')] opacity-10 z-0"></div>
  
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 relative z-10 font-mono">
    <!-- Classified Stamp -->
    <div class="border-4 border-indigo-500/50 p-2 inline-block rounded mb-12 transform rotate-2 opacity-80">
      <div class="text-indigo-500 font-black text-2xl uppercase tracking-[0.2em]">Authorized</div>
      <div class="text-indigo-500/80 font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-wider text-center">Protocol: Alpha</div>
    </div>

    <!-- Header -->
    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-white mb-8 tracking-tighter uppercase decoration-indigo-500 underline decoration-4 underline-offset-8">
      Mission Directive
    </h1>

    <div class="prose prose-invert prose-indigo max-w-none space-y-8">
      
      <div class="bg-gray-800/50 border border-gray-700/50 p-6 rounded-lg backdrop-blur-sm">
        <p class="text-xs font-bold text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-4 border-b border-gray-700 pb-2">Directive ID: TERMS-2025-Y</p>
        
        <p class="leading-relaxed">
          <span class="font-bold text-white">1. Acceptance of Orders</span><br>
          By accessing this Mission Control platform ("DoneYet"), you agree to follow all operational protocols defined herein. Failure to comply may result in immediate revocation of your license to kill (bugs).
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="relative pl-6 border-l border-gray-700">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">2. Agent Responsibilities</h3>
        <p class="mb-2">As an operative, you are responsible for:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-1">
           <li>Maintaining security of your login credentials.</li>
           <li>Reporting hostile incursions (system errors) immediately.</li>
           <li>Using agency resources only for sanctioned missions.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="relative pl-6 border-l border-gray-700">
         <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">3. Liability Protocol</h3>
         <p>
           The Agency is not responsible for burned aliases, failed missions due to incompetence, or coffee spills on agency equipment. We provide the tools; you provide the talent.
         </p>
      </div>

      <div class="relative pl-6 border-l border-gray-700">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">4. Contract Termination</h3>
        <p>You may abort your mission (cancel subscription) at any time. We do not require a burn notice. However, no refunds on deployed assets.</p>
      </div>

    </div>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <div class="mt-16 pt-8 border-t border-gray-800 flex justify-between items-end">
       <div class="text-xs text-gray-500 font-mono">
         <p>APPROVED BY: FERNANDO LEANO</p>
         <p>DATE: 2025-12-23</p>
       </div>
       <%= image_tag "logo.svg", class: "w-12 h-12 opacity-20 grayscale", alt: "Watermark" %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
